The second NPC tells you that you can use words and runes to make new spells, he specifically says that you use 1 word and 1 rune for each combination. Seems straightforward enough, words and runes probably drop off the new planer mobs of course. <br>
The third NPC is the hardest to decipher. He tells you that you must &quot;combine 4 scrolls of the same power, belonging to different arcane circles&quot; he further tells you that you will have better luck making higher level spells if you understand how they work. Once you do this it says that it will divide the spells up into there separate notes and you are supposed to give them to his apprentices. he also says that the spells you need to use are between the 10th and the 14th circles, or level 39 to 52 spells<br>
<br>
Lets brainstorm on how to complete these spells =)<br>
<br>
